  "text": "annotation were performed by the DOE Joint Genome Institute (JGI) using state of the art sequencing technology [CITATION_1] . A summary of the project information is shown in Table 2 . . DNA was isolated from 0.5-1 g of cell paste using JetFlex Genomic DNA Purification Kit (GENOMED) following the standard protocol as recommended by the manufacturer, however with additional 50 μl protease K (20 mg/ml) during digest for 60 min. at 58°C. Protein precipitation was done with additional 200 μl Protein Precipitation Buffer, followed by over night incubation on ice. DNA is available through the DNA Bank Network [CITATION_2] .",
